@node Main "Brikon - Documentation"

                              'Brikon' 1.03

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Brikon' is a @{" Workbench game " link play} played on an 8 by 8 tile board. The
idea is to place 32 bricks in such a way that there are no continuous
straight lines between bricks, from one edge of the board to the
other.

  To complicate matters a little, from 1 to 8 bricks are already
placed on the game board, and when a brick is placed, it cannot be
moved later on...

  Have fun!

